summary: 该插件用于检测泛微E-Mobile6.0的client.do接口是否存在命令执行漏洞，通过发送特定POST请求验证是否可以成功执行命令。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the client.do interface of Fanwei E-Mobile 6.0 has a command execution vulnerability by sending a specific POST request to verify if commands can be executed successfully.
